TestTool.Model.TestTaking

Class StudentAnswer

  • java.lang.Object
    • TestTool.Model.TestTaking.StudentAnswer

  • public abstract class StudentAnswer
extends java.lang.Object
    StudentAnswer Class is a class that allows individual question types to be linked together. It act as a parent class so it will be easier to access the different question types. This class have a variable named "QuestionNumber". It is used to keep track of which number the question is student answering and which question the software is checking.
